@MattHancock We're losing .France reported 115 new coronavirus cases on 24 May 9 in Australia on 25 May. In the UK, 1625 new cases were reported on 25 May. The ONS estimates that 61,000 new infections a week occurred in England between 4 and 17 May.

Read more: https://t.co/Z9fw7pA92t
